{"id":"54508d98-80c4-4f9e-aef7-deec3fb8c525","name":"Goro Majima","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\"A Gilded Cage.\"<img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/ELJyjrOgaQT6hGw7AfSNw.gif\" style=\"width: 284.5px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">\"Rather lose an eye than bow to you, bitch.\"</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/UAxr-cqlz9qwnAOnwL_j4.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(229, 16, 16);\"><strong>Goro Majima</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"> (真島 吾朗, <em>Majima Gorō</em>) is a recurring major character in the </span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://yakuza.fandom.com/wiki/Like_a_Dragon\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(229, 16, 16);\"><em>Like a Dragon</em></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(229, 16, 16);\"> (formerly <em>Yakuza</em>) series</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"> introduced in the original </span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://yakuza.fandom.com/wiki/Yakuza\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><em>Yakuza</em></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">. He is featured as a protagonist in </span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://yakuza.fandom.com/wiki/Yakuza_0\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(229, 16, 16);\"><em>Yakuza 0</em></span></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/HNwVgM881M-VY-Mf-LTf5.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">His unpredictability, ferocity in combat, and accomplishments as the captain of the </span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://yakuza.fandom.com/wiki/Shimano_Family\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(229, 16, 16);\">Shimano Family</span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"> earned him the nickname \"</span><span style=\"color: rgb(229, 16, 16);\">The Mad Dog of Shimano</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">\"</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/tUvUs9v45Tw67arFeV555.gif\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><em>\"I'll do anything. Revenge, you name it. Whatever you want! So please... please...!\"</em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/e1uq4b_O7oVmh_4AYK6p9.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"2aa17f79-0e24-4a7c-b400-0786fd6d79c9_64db7ab2-83f6-468b-9147-5e761a4e19b6.webp","creator":"The TiredTimes","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","📚 Fictional","🎮 Game"],"chats":1202,"messages":32979,"created_at":"2024-11-24T03:26:51.092720+00:00"}